\MyProject\LolitaFramework\Core\Img::url
===

Get image URL.

Example usage
---
```php
$src = Img::url();
// htt://somesite.com/someimage.jpg

```
Parameters
---
**$attachment_id** (int) (optional) attachment id. Default: 0.

**$size** (string) (optional) image size. Default: thumbnail.

Return Value
---
**string** 
